    simpa using (Real.continuous_sinc.tendsto 0).const_mul r |>.comp ((tendsto_id 0).const_mul r)
  refine tendsto_nhdsWithin_congr (fun x hx => ?_) (h.mono_left inf_le_left)
  simp [Real.sinc_apply, hx]
  split_ifs with hrx
  · simp [hrx]
  · field_simp [hrx]; ring
```
